Made in limited numbers! Let’s be accurate 250 of each design!
After returning home to Melbourne and seeing it through new eyes, with an increased level of appreciation for how it's shaped us and Ottway, we took the opportunity of this campaign to create a design truly remarkable!

Pulled from the archives of a classic old & worn 70's bomber jacket, the 𝐁𝐢𝐥𝐥𝐲 𝐁𝐨𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 was built to last, full of Ottway detail appreciation and sustainably made. It's design will forever be timeless, with our reputable craftsmanship at it's finest and fit for where ever you'll take it!

